  "instructions": [
    "heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add dried oregano and thyme, if using, and cook for 1 minute, until herbs are fragrant.",
    "add sliced renkon-lotus-root and cook for 3-4 minutes, until lightly browned.",
    "season with salt and pepper, to taste.",
    "add lemon juice and toss to combine.",
    "cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, until renkon-lotus-root is crispy and golden brown.",
    "shave bonito flakes on top of the renkon-lotus-root mixture.",
    "garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot."
